# Hugging Face: on each gated model card, accept user conditions FIRST, then create a token at:
# https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
# Use Read access only (enough to download public/gated models; Write is not required).
# Fine-grained: grant Read on the Hub repos you need, or use a classic Read token.
# Gated diarization (default): https://huggingface.co/pyannote/speaker-diarization-community-1
HF_TOKEN=

